fields.name: TXT_Error
fields.fieldText:
It looks like this contact may already exist in the system. Please click 'Next' and enter new details or select a contact from the list at the bottom of the screen.


Alternatively, close this process and add a contact to the Account manually.

fields.name: TXT_Screen1
fields.fieldText:
You are about to prepare a Contract for the below Quote.


{!VAR_Syncd_Quote_Name}


Please ensure that this is the correct Quote to use.


ï»¿If it isn't, you can select 'Yes' below to change the quote.

fields.name: TXT_Screen4a
fields.fieldText:
You must select 1 and only 1 quote term to take forward for contract.


Please click 'Previous' and update your selection.

fields.name: Select_the_Quote_you_want_to_use
fields.fieldText: Select the Quote you want to use

fields.name: TXT_Screen3
fields.fieldText:
ere are the commercial details of the quote you have selected. Please review the details and ensure that they are correct before proceeding.


Start Date: {!VAR_Start_Date}


Number of Utility Accounts Quoted: {!VAR_Accounts_Quoted}


If you need to update any of these details, please go to the Quote record and make the necessary changes.

fields.name: TXT_Screen4
fields.fieldText: Only 1 quote term can be taken through to contract.

fields.name: TXT_Screen4_2
fields.fieldText: Please note that upon clicking 'Next', all other quote terms will be deleted.

fields.name: TXT_Screen5
fields.fieldText:
Customer Contract is created and ready to be sent to the Customer for Signature.


Thanks!

fields.name: TXT_Screen6
fields.fieldText:
There is no primary contact on this customer. Please complete the below fields to create one.


This is the person who will be sent the supply agreement to sign (by default).

fields.name: TXT_Screen_6_2
fields.fieldText: Alternatively, you can select an existing Contact from this customer to set as the Primary Contact:

fields.name: TXT_Screenx
fields.fieldText:
You must enter a contact first name, last name and email address to create a new contact.


Alternatively, you can select an existing contact from the list at the bottom of the screen.


Click 'Next' and try again.
